                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.10">
                                <locus from="31ra" to="35ra"></locus>
                                <title ref="LIT1295Dersan#MiracleNahase">Healing of the Blind</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተአምሪሁ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወሀሎ፡ ክርስቲያናዊ፡ በውስተ፡ አሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ 
                                    ወረከቦ፡ ፅፁበ፡ ደዌ፡ ወዖራ፡ ክልኤሆን፡ አዕይንቲሁ፡.
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.11">
                                <locus from="35ra" to="40vb"></locus>
                                <title ref="LIT1295Dersan#MiracleMaskaram">Dorotheus and Theophista find 300 coins in a fish</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተበህለ፡ ከመ፡ ሀሎ፡ ብእሲ፡ በአሐቲ፡ ሀገር፡ እምአህጉረ፡ ግብጽ፡ ዘትሰመይ፡ እስክንድርያ፡ 
                                    ወይሰመ፡ ይ፡ ውእቱ፡ ድራትዮስ፡ ወስመ፡ ብእሲቱ፡ ቲዎብስታ፡<cb n="b"/> ወ፪ሆሙ፡ ፈራህያነ፡ 
                                    አግዚአብሔር፡.
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.12">
                                <locus from="40vb" to="44vb"></locus>
                                <title ref="LIT1295Dersan#MiracleYakkatit">Of the poor man who, once enriched thanks to money borrowed from a bishop in charge of a church, returns this money to the church guardian via a fish</title>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ተአምሪሁ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/> ተብህለ፡ ካፅበ፡ ከመ፡ ሀሎ፡ ነዳይ፡ ወበጥቃሁ፡ ትነብር፡ ቤተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ 
                                    ዘሕንጽት፡ በስሙ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ወይስእል፡ በአንብዕ፡ ወይብል፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/>.
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="44vb" to="90rb"></locus>
                            <title ref="LIT4652TaammeraGa">19 miracles of the Archangel Gabriel</title>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.1">
                                <locus from="44vb" to="46va"></locus>
                                <title type="complete" ref="LIT4654MiracleGa"/>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    <pb n="44vb"/>በስመ፡<gap reason="ellipsis"/><pb n="45ra"/> ተአምሪሁ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወእንዘ፡ የከርዩ፡ አውሪዶሙ፡ 
                                    መጠነ፡ ቆመ፡ ብ<gap reason="ellipsis"/> እሲ፡ ወፅአ፡ <cb n="b"/> ዘዲበ፡ ርእሱ፡ አቅርንት፡ ወነሰኮ፡ 
                                    ለዘይከሪ፡ ወመልአ፡ ሕምዙ፡ ኩለንታሁ፡ ወሞተ።
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i2.2">
                                <locus from="46va" to="48va"></locus>
                                <title type="complete" ref="LIT4655MiracleGa"/>
                                <note>For 19 Tahsās</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    <pb n="46va"/>፪ ተአም<gap reason="ellipsis"/>ሪሁ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/> ወእንዘ፡ የሐንጹ፡ ወይጸውሩ፡ 
